divs: Sighting DetailsWhen I 6 years old, I was at home playing in my backyard when my mother called me inside for lunch. I was running towards the back door when I noticed something in the sky on the left above (at very low cloud level) my neighbours house. I stopped and looked at the object for a good 15 seconds before I got scared and ran inside. The object was spherical, with pincer-like arms coming out of either side. There was a large black window and the rest was white with some black on the pincers.It wasn't making a sound but the pincers were moving slowly pulling at or separating a cloud. Whilst watching the object I felt really scared so I ran inside and didn't tell anyone until I saw more UFOs as an adult and understood what they were.

Summary: Spherical UFO with pincers was stationary above my neighbours house.
